data.title: Popeye Filmography
data.text:
The following is a filmography of the Popeye cartoons which came out of the Max Fleischer and Paramount Studios between the years of 1933 and 1957. Thanks go to Leonard Maltin for his book Of Mice and Magic which was my primary source. Please note that there may be small errors on this page which were corrected in the episode guide. I am still working on making sure these two lists match. If in doubt, rely on the episode guide.
